		<h2 class='diff-currentversion-title'>Revision as of 22:25, 4 September 2014</h2>
<div class="hatnote">This article is about the harmonic oscillator in classical mechanics.  For its uses in <a href="/wiki/Quantum_mechanics" title="Quantum mechanics">quantum mechanics</a>, see <a href="/wiki/Quantum_harmonic_oscillator" title="Quantum harmonic oscillator">quantum harmonic oscillator</a>.</div>
