<th width="225" align="left"><a href="/wiki/RLC_Circuit#Series_RLC_circuit" title="RLC Circuit" class="mw-redirect">Series RLC Circuit</a></th>
<th width="225" align="left"><a href="/wiki/RLC_Circuit#Parallel_RLC_circuit" title="RLC Circuit" class="mw-redirect">Parallel RLC Circuit</a></th>
</tr>
<tr>
